dataIdInfo.idPurp: Administrative Level 0-2 and Operational Zones Level 1-2 Lines of Somalia

dataLineage.statement:
Administrative boundary lines for the Administrative Level 0-2 and Operational Zones Level 1-2 of Somalia. The lines were created after all processing on the admin layer had been completed by ITOS.
An 'AdminLevel' field is used to attribute the lines. The values used for this field are: (0,1,2,3,4,5,87,88,99). 99 represents coastline. 0 is international border, 1 is Admin1 border, 2 is Admin2 border, 3 is OPZ1, 4 is OPZ2. Each line is attributed with the highest admin level that it can participate in.
